{
  "stem": "13198.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] of course, at the background was always this Jewish thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went to church every Sunday with our nanny.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was sent to boarding school when I was five years old with-- my elder sister was at the same boarding school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Church was all day long on Sunday at that boarding school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, we went to church in the morning at 11 o'clock and children's service in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the-- the girls that were over 10, I think, went in the evening again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, there was hymn singing after supper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and I want to call it grace before meals and grace after.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was sort of religion all the time dinned into you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just took it for granted, like that was the way it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I wanted to-- I knew that I wasn't baptized, so I thought I wouldn't go to heaven, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I thought I better get baptized pretty quickly-- christened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew it was a great, big thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I knew my parents wouldn't like this, because they didn't want to be involved in any religious thing, neither Christian nor-- they just said, do what everybody else does.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was sort of the way they went about things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so when I had to say to my parents, look, I want to be christened, I was really frightened.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I thought they might make a fuss.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I remember plucking up courage and saying, look.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I want to be christened in a church.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said, oh, well, if that's what you want, go ahead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'd built up this great thing, and it wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
